1.   A movie theater. 2.   Movies collectively, especially when considered as an art form. 1.   (Film)  chiefly   a.  a place designed for the exhibition of films b.  ( as modifier ):  a cinema seat .  2.   (Film)  the cinema  a.  the art or business of making films b.  films collectively    1.    the cinema,  motion pictures, as an art or industry.     2.   a motion-picture theater. 